* Google=E2=80=99s Spotify Deal, The Ideal App Store Approach, Spotify=E2=
=80=99s South Korea Option ( https://stratechery.com/2022/googles-spotify-d=
eal-the-ideal-app-store-approach-spotifys-south-korea-option/ ) =E2=80=94 G=
oogle and Spotify=E2=80=99s deal is light on details, but it=E2=80=99s clea=
r who the big winners are. See also: Spotify Earnings, Spotify Exclusives, =
Spotify vs. Apple ( https://stratechery.com/2022/spotify-earnings-spotify-e=
xclusives-spotify-vs-apple/ ).
* Law Enforcement and User Data, Tradeoffs and Trust, Centralization and En=
cryption ( https://stratechery.com/2022/law-enforcement-and-user-data-trade=
offs-and-trust-centralization-and-encryption/ ) =E2=80=94 A story about how=
 hackers got data from tech companies illustrates the fundamental challenge=
 of trust on the Internet, and gives insight into the challenges of interop=
erability.
* Amazon Earnings, Amazon=E2=80=99s Costs, Amazon Closes Stores ( https://s=
tratechery.com/2022/amazon-earnings-amazons-costs-amazon-closes-stores/ ) =
=E2=80=94 Amazon messed up its capacity planning and the result was a big l=
oss; CEO Andy Jassy seems focused on scalability above everything else.
* Shopify Earnings, Shopify Acquires Deliverr, Shopify and Buy With Prime (=
 https://stratechery.com/2022/shopify-earnings-shopify-acquires-deliverr-sh=
opify-and-buy-with-prime/ ) =E2=80=94 Shopify=E2=80=99s earnings were disap=
pointing; worse, they were confusing. The company knows its mission, but ne=
eds to clarify its strategy. See also: this Update about Shopify Audiences =
( https://stratechery.com/2022/shopify-follow-up-shopify-audiences-unity-ea=
rnings/ ) , and this Update about Shopify vs Buy With Prime ( https://strat=
echery.com/2022/shopify-vs-buy-with-prime-instagram-shopping-cuda-and-china=
/ ).
