 Takeaways ( https://stratechery.com/2022/snap-revenue-warning-snaps-direct=
-response-bifurcation-broader-takeaways/ ) =E2=80=94 Snap=E2=80=99s revenue=
 warning, and a closer examination of past earnings, point to a business th=
at is much more driven by brand advertising than it is by direct response.
