stratechery.com/2022/nvidia-warning-nvidia-vs-tsmc-ethereum-miners-vs-the-m=
erge/ ) =E2=80=94 Nvidia released an earnings warning that was bad on the s=
urface and even worse in the details; one of the reasons to be bearish is t=
he Ethereum Merge.
